<p>Google Developer Groups from the UK &amp; Ireland have banded together for this year's DevFest, a multi-track event covering:</p><p>- Cloud<br>- AI/Machine Learning<br>- Web<br>- Mobile<br>- Emerging/Hot Tech<br>- Diversity, Equity &amp; Inclusion</p><p>DevFest 2020 brings together thousands of developers globally for the largest virtual weekend of community-led technical learning and a shared passion for Google technologies.</p><p>The magic of DevFest has always come from the people involved - developers from all different backgrounds and skill levels.</p><p>For DevFest 2020, Google Developer Groups are coming together in a whole new way - virtually over one weekend. This global moment empowers developers to teach, learn, and connect when they may need it the most.</p></p>
